CreatePaymentPlan.js → for creating new plans.

PaymentPlanList.js → for listing all plans with Edit and Delete buttons.

EditPaymentPlan.js → for editing an existing plan.


POST /api/payment-plans/ → Create a payment plan

GET /api/payment-plans/ → List all payment plans

GET /api/payment-plans/<id>/ → Get details of one

PUT/PATCH /api/payment-plans/<id>/ → Update

DELETE /api/payment-plans/<id>/ → Delete

